                <pre class="mainprices">280 EGP</pre>
            </div>

            <div class="main-dishes-item">
                <img class="mainimg" src="Images/STEAK AND ENCHILADAS.jpg" alt="Steak and Enchiladas image">
                <h2 class="mainnames">STEAK AND ENCHILADAS</h2>
                <p class="maindescription">Tender steak paired with flavorful enchiladas, a hearty choice for any occasion.</p>
                <pre class="mainprices">600 EGP</pre>
            </div>

            <div class="main-dishes-item">
                <img class="mainimg" src="Images/CHICKEN TAMPIQUENA.jpg" alt="Chicken Tampiquena image">
                <h2 class="mainnames">CHICKEN TAMPIQUENA <span class="spicy">(Spicy)</span></h2>
                <p class="maindescription">Spicy grilled chicken served with traditional sides, a Tex-Mex favorite.</p>
                <pre class="mainprices">290 EGP</pre>
            </div>

            <div class="main-dishes-item">
                <img class="mainimg" src="Images/Tilapia.jpg" alt="Tilapia image">
                <h2 class="mainnames">TILAPIA</h2>
                <p class="maindescription">Fresh tilapia fillet seasoned and grilled to perfection, served with your choice of sides.</p>
                <pre class="mainprices">400 EGP</pre>
            </div>

            <div class="main-dishes-item">
                <img class="mainimg" src="Images/FAJITA TACOS.jpg" alt="Fajita Tacos image">
                <h2 class="mainnames">FAJITA TACOS</h2>
                <p class="maindescription">Sizzling fajita meat served in soft tortillas with fresh toppings and a side of salsa.</p>
                <pre class="mainprices">200 EGP</pre>
            </div>
